high_descs: Go forward, turn right, go forward, turn left, turn left to the edge of the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right and go to the counter to the right of the stove
Slice the tomato on the counter
Turn left and go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn right, go forward, turn left after the stove
Pick up a tomato slice from the counter
Turn left and go to the fridge
Put the tomato slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the fridge
Turn right, go forward, turn left after the stove
Put the tomato slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato and cool a slice of it

high_descs: Turn right then right again and face the counter to your right.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the counter in front of you.
Slice the tomato above the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge to your right.
Place the knife inside of the fridge in front of you and close it.
Turn right and face the counter to your left.
Take a tomato slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge to your right.
Place the tomato inside of the fridge then take it out.
Turn right and face the counter to your left.
Place the tomato slice on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Walk forward, turn right, walk to the far wall, and turn around to face the knife on the center island.
Pick up the knife from the center island.
Walk to the counter next to the stove.
Cut the tomato on the counter with the knife.
Take the knife to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Go back to the tomato slices on the counter.
Pick up a tomato slice from the counter.
Take the tomato to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and take it back out.
Take the tomato slice back to the counter it came from.
Set the tomato slice down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Slice and refrigerate a slice of the tomato that is on the counter next to the stove.
